# Spotify API Credentials
# Get these from: https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard

SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id_here
SPOTIFY_CLIENT_SECRET=your_client_secret_here

# Instructions:
# 1. Go to https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard
# 2. Log in with your Spotify account
# 3. Click "Create app"
# 4. Fill in app name: "mxster Card Generator"
# 5. Fill in app description: "Generates game cards for mxster music game"
# 6. Redirect URI: Not needed (use Client Credentials flow)
# 7. Check "Web API" in APIs used
# 8. Copy Client ID and Client Secret
# 9. Create a .env file (copy this file) and paste your credentials
# 10. Run: node add-song.js "<spotify-url>"
